T02D2384:18b-3: rin chen phreng ba zhes bya ba /
T02D2384:18b-4: dpal he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2384:18b-5: mgon po kun gyi bdag nyid ni //
T02D2384:18b-6: dngos po'i rang bzhin ma grub pa'i //
T02D2384:18b-7: bla ma rje la phyag 'tshal nas //
T02D2384:18b-8: rin chen phreng ba bshad par bya //
T02D2384:18b-9: bsgom dang sgom rgyu rnal 'byor gyi //
T02D2384:18b-10: rtog pa de ni bden pa min //
T02D2384:18b-11: bden gnyis grub pa med pa'i phyir //
T02D2384:18b-12: sgom la brten par mi bya'o //
T02D2384:18b-13: chos kyi dbyings dang de bzhin nyid //
T02D2384:18b-14: gang yang rang bzhin rtogs pa de //
T02D2384:18b-15: zhi ba rang rig gnyis su med //
T02D2384:18b-16: bla ma dam pa'i dgongs pa'o //
T02D2384:18b-17: mtshan nyid med pa'i shes rab ni //
T02D2384:18b-18: phyag rgya bla ma'i gdams ngag bcas //
T02D2384:18b-19: phra zhing rang rgyud ye shes kyi //
T02D2384:18b-20: ma rdzogs pa yi skad cig la //
T02D2384:18b-21: yang dag grub par mi 'gyur ro //
T02D2384:18b-22: bla ma gnyis pa'i dgongs pa'o //
T02D2384:18b-23: rnam par rtog pa bden pa min //
T02D2384:18b-24: rtog med rjes su 'brel pa yi //
T02D2384:18b-25: rim gyis rnam rtog rnams dang bral //
T02D2384:18b-26: dper na tha gu sbrul 'dzin te //
T02D2384:18b-27: rnal 'byor rtog med bde ba che //
T02D2384:18b-28: bla ma gsum pa'i dgongs pa'o //
T02D2384:18b-29: ma rig pa yi snang ba 'di //
T02D2384:19a-0: @19a * // rang rig ye shes rtogs gyur na //
T02D2384:19a-1: rmi lam nyin mo'i snang ba rnams //
T02D2384:19a-2: mnyam pa nyid du don rtogs pas //
T02D2384:19a-3: tshor ba tshor byed gnyis su med //
T02D2384:19a-4: gnyis dang gnyis min spangs pa yi //
T02D2384:19a-5: gang la mi gnas rnal 'byor de //
T02D2384:19a-6: shes rab pha rol phyin pa yin //
T02D2384:19a-7: bla ma bzhi pa'i dgongs pa'o //
T02D2384:19a-8: bdag nyid sha la'o dgongs pa ni //
T02D2384:19a-9: dmigs med snying rje'i rnal 'byor ba //
T02D2384:19a-10: gnyis 'dzin gnyis med don rtogs can //
T02D2384:19a-11: zab mo'i chos nyid la gnas pas //
T02D2384:19a-12: rdo rje sems dpa'i gnas thob 'gyur //
T02D2384:19a-13: rtog pa dang bral dri ma med //
T02D2384:19a-14: rnal 'byor rol pa'i lta spyod ni //
T02D2384:19a-15: chos rnams rang bzhin rtogs gyur na //
T02D2384:19a-16: bde dang sdug bsngal gnyis med rtogs //
T02D2384:19a-17: de ltar rtogs pas rang grol 'gyur //
